lead_paragraph: Two-time Olympic pole vault champion Yelena Isinbayeva is among four candidates to register for an election to choose a new president of the All-Russian Athletics Federation (ARAF), the organization said on its official website.

headline.print_headline: Isinbayeva to Face Three Opponents in Bid to Become Russian Athletics Chief
headline.main: Isinbayeva to Face Three Opponents in Bid to Become Russian Athletics Chief
